runtimeAttrs.Sql Override:
SELECT partyid, oscregistryid, countrycode, resourceid, reptype FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT a.partyid as partyid, a.oscregistryid as oscregistryid, a.countrycode as countrycode, c.partyid as resourceid, 'BusinessPartnerInVitro_c' as reptype
from osc.t_osc_org a, osc.t_osc_rep_asgn_rule b, osc.t_osc_resource c
where a.countrycode = b.countrycode and b.listofreps = 'BusinessPartnerInVitro_c' and b.active = 'Y'and a.businesspartnerinvitroid is not null and a.businesspartnerinvitroid = c.resourceprofileid
MINUS
SELECT DISTINCT b.partyid as partyid, b.oscregistryid as oscregistryid, b.countrycode as countrycode, c.partyid as resourceid, 'BusinessPartnerInVitro_c' as reptype
FROM osc.t_osc_accnt_resource a, osc.t_osc_org b, osc.t_osc_resource c, osc.t_osc_rep_asgn_rule d
WHERE a.sales_account_id = b.salesaccountid and a.resource_id = c.partyid and b.countrycode = d.countrycode and d.listofreps = 'BusinessPartnerInVitro_c' and d.active = 'Y' and b.businesspartnerinvitroid is not null
UNION ALL
